{"tid":1543313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唱do you hear 成日都聽唔到會唱依段","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T09:04:13.000Z","uid":69293,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6b43d1d0bc2f8ab78442daf869be1ad858d93c","tid":1543313,"uid":69293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"每次聽到大家唱的時候好多都係唱<br />\nDo you hear the people sing?<br />\nSinging a song of angry men?<br />\nIt is the music of a people<br />\nWho will not be slaves again!<br />\nWhen the beating of your heart<br />\nEchoes the beating of the drums<br />\nThere is a life about to start<br />\nWhen tomorrow comes!<br />\n<br />\n之後再繼續loop,但成日覺得下一段先係靈魂<br />\n唔單只係表達憤怒而係要爭取自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWill you join in our crusade?<br />\nWho will be strong and stand with me?<br />\nBeyond the barricade<br />\nIs there a world you long to see?<br />\nThen join in the fight<br />\nThat will give you the right to be free!<br />\n<br />\n下次大家唱埋依一段好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a364549263fcaacefe06930b95b28f2c38741d89","tid":1543313,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:45:34.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=